title: Welcome!
text:
Welcome to my personal website that I created by using Quarto in Rstudio. My name is Jack Freimann. I am a Sophomore at Macalester College pursuing a major in Economics and minors in Political Science and Statistics. Please take a look at this website if you are interested in learning more about some of my interests and past work.





During the year, I spend a lot of time playing soccer. For the school year I am a member of the Macalester Men’s Soccer team.

 

Some of my other interests include, fishing, traveling, the Denver Nuggets, playing the guitar, and spending time with family and friends. I hope you enjoy learning more about me!
